                              <p>
                                To list an item for sale on <strong>kenaBecha.com</strong>, please follow these steps:
                              </p>
                              <ol>
                                <li>
                                  <strong>Login or Signup:</strong> You need to have an account. If youâ€™re not logged in, use the "Login" or "Sign-up" option in the top-right corner of the website.
                                </li>
                                <li>
