                                </li>
                                <li>
                                  <strong>Navigate to Upload Item:</strong> After logging in, click on the <strong>Upload Item</strong> option in the navigation bar.
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                  <strong>Fill the Upload Form:</strong>
                                  Provide the following details about your product:
                                  <ul>
                                    <li>Upload a cover photo and additional pictures of the product.</li>
                                    <li>Enter the product name, price, and description.</li>
                                    <li>Provide your contact number and the product's location.</li>
                                  </ul>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                  <strong>Submit the Form:</strong> Once all the details are filled in, click on the "Submit Form" button.
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                  <strong>Listed Successfully:</strong> Your product will now be listed in the catalog and visible to other users.
                                </li>
                              </ol>
                              <p>
